Welcome

Welcome to the Iowa Electrical Licensing and Inspection website. From this site you will be able to apply for an electrician license, renew your license, get a duplicate license, create and view your personal license account, purchase an electrical permit, or request inspections by clicking on the appropriate icon to the right.

  • For more information on electrician licensing and permitting/inspections please visit the State Fire Marshal’s website.
  • To find out who does the permitting and inspections in your area visit our interactive county map and click on the county where you are working.
